  "body": "`ReactNativeComponent` currently uses `findNodeHandle` and `mountSafeCallback`. The former is not desirable. The latter is bad because now that `View` and `Text` have been upgraded to extend `ReactNativeComponent`, `mountSafeCallback` uses `isMounted` and triggers the React warning.\r\n\r\nThis resolves the issue by requiring that subclasses assign `this.nativeRef` to the root element's `ref` prop.",
